Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.43,0:00:24.26,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur3\be3}一直在寻找真理
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.51,0:00:28.60,op_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)\blur3\be3}却在彷徨中迷失了方向
